Geraldine Duenas –  Graduate Counselor, Professional Programs
Lumen Russell – Instructional Support Manager
Madhu Reddy – Associate Dean for Graduate Student AffairsPlease contact the Associate Dean for Graduate Student Affairs at gadsa@ics.uci.edu to discuss concerns (not related to specific academic advising), or share your thoughts and recommendations about any aspect of the ICS graduate program.




